 <i>worthy of you. </i>

00:30:07.630 --> 00:30:12.769 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>When I first grasped the</i>
 <i>Xenian Flower, I realized...</i>

00:30:12.803 --> 00:30:17.508 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>...those heartless humans on</i>
 <i>Earth who disregarded you</i>
 <i>and left you all alone...</i>

00:30:17.542 --> 00:30:19.644 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>must be annihilated! </i>

00:30:25.551 --> 00:30:30.824 position:16% line:83% align:start
 Fiore... I never wanted
that at all. Why are you-?

00:30:34.762 --> 00:30:36.397 position:5% line:89% align:start
Mamoru...

00:30:36.730 --> 00:30:40.034 position:5% line:83% align:start
You wouldn't... leave me all
alone, would you?

00:30:40.067 --> 00:30:41.403 position:35% line:89% align:start
Fiore...

00:30:43.003 --> 00:30:46.642 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm the only one who's
allowed to give you flowers.

00:30:48.678 --> 00:30:51.648 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Just what is this Xenian</i>
 <i>Flower, anyway? </i>

00:30:52.114 --> 00:30:56.119 position:13% line:77% align:start
It's an evil plant... that
wants to drain the energy
from every last planet.

00:30:56.520 --> 00:30:58.957 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's the universe's most
dangerous life form.

00:30:58.989 --> 00:31:02.962 position:10% line:77% align:start
This is the first time both
Artemis and I have seen a
real one.

00:31:02.994 --> 00:31:07.633 position:10% line:77% align:start
But even long ago, way back
in the Moon Kingdom, we had
heard all kinds of legends

00:31:07.666 --> 00:31:09.268 position:13% line:89% align:start
about the Xenian Flower.

00:31:09.301 --> 00:31:12.906 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>The flower itself is just a</i>
 <i>plant, so it isn't able to</i>
 <i>move. </i>

00:31:13.173 --> 00:31:17.143 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>It needs people or other</i>
 <i>creatures to act as its arms</i>
 <i>and legs. </i>

00:31:17.177 --> 00:31:21.015 position:21% line:77% align:start
 <i>So the Xenian Flower</i>
 <i>possesses people who are</i>
 <i>weak-minded. </i>

00:31:21.048 --> 00:31:23.150 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>Weak-minded...? </i>

00:31:23.184 --> 00:31:28.156 position:10% line:77% align:start
Once possessed, their heart
becomes filled with hatred
and produces evil power.

00:31:39.069 --> 00:31:43.008 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>The planets that have been</i>
 <i>destroyed by the Xenian</i>
 <i>Flower in this galaxy alone</i>

00:31:43.040 --> 00:31:44.844 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>are too numerous to count. </i>

00:31:45.110 --> 00:31:47.847 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then that person who
snatched Mamoru away...

00:31:47.880 --> 00:31:50.716 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yes! He's possessed by the
Xenian Flower.

00:31:50.750 --> 00:31:54.120 position:5% line:77% align:start
I analyzed the energy from
the monster we fought this
morning.

00:31:54.153 --> 00:31:57.792 position:5% line:77% align:start
It turns out that the
asteroid that is now
approaching the Earth is

00:31:57.825 --> 00:32:00.060 position:5% line:83% align:start
emitting the same energy as
this flower.

00:32:00.093 --> 00:32:01.529 position:38% line:89% align:start
 What?!

00:32:01.563 --> 00:32:03.231 position:16% line:83% align:start
Then that asteroid must
be...

00:32:03.264 --> 00:32:05.935 position:10% line:83% align:start
There's no doubt! The Xenian
hideout!

00:32:05.968 --> 00:32:09.505 position:5% line:83% align:start
And that has to be the place
where Mamoru has been taken!

00:32:09.538 --> 00:32:11.041 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then there's no time to
waste!

00:32:11.073 --> 00:32:13.577 position:5% line:83% align:start
Let's all teleport to the
asteroid!

00:32:13.610 --> 00:32:17.582 position:5% line:77% align:start
Destroying the Xenian Flower
is the only way to save
Earth!

00:32:17.615 --> 00:32:18.616 position:38% line:89% align:start
No way!

00:32:18.649 --> 00:32:19.584 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:32:20.819 --> 00:32:23.722 position:16% line:77% align:start
We can't go up there! We
can't take big risks like
that...

00:32:24.957 --> 00:32:28.995 position:10% line:83% align:start
'Cause otherwise, you could
all end up like Mamo...

00:32:30.029 --> 00:32:34.133 position:19% line:89% align:start
This is all my fault!

00:32:34.167 --> 00:32:37.605 position:19% line:77% align:start
Poor Mamo, he got hurt
because he tried to protect
me...

00:32:39.741 --> 00:32:40.942 position:5% line:89% align:start
Usagi...

00:32:40.976 --> 00:32:41.643 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Hey! </i>

00:32:41.676 --> 00:32:42.544 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh?

00:32:43.411 --> 00:32:45.580 position:19% line:83% align:start
Get ahold of yourself!
Sailor Moon!

00:32:49.685 --> 00:32:52.121 position:10% line:83% align:start
How do you expect to rescue
him like that?

00:32:52.856 --> 00:32:54.024 position:44% line:89% align:start
Eh--

00:32:59.262 --> 00:33:02.101 position:19% line:83% align:start
A Guardian of Justice
doesn't cry!

00:33:02.133 --> 00:33:03.936 position:30% line:89% align:start
Chibi-Usa...

00:33:03.969 --> 00:33:06.105 position:10% line:83% align:start
You know, Chibi-Usa's right,
Usagi.

00:33:06.137 --> 00:33:08.975 position:5% line:83% align:start
Earth is being threatened by
a powerful enemy.

00:33:09.009 --> 00:33:11.778 position:10% line:83% align:start
here's no time to feel sorry
for yourself!

00:33:11.811 --> 00:33:12.679 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:33:13.747 --> 00:33:15.850 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's for Mamoru's sake, too.

00:33:17.718 --> 00:33:19.887 position:35% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:33:33.603 --> 00:33:34.570 position:35% line:89% align:start
Sailor...

00:33:34.605 --> 00:33:35.973 position:30% line:89% align:start
...Teleport!

00:33:58.900 --> 00:34:00.935 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>Usagi... Good luck... </i>

00:34:13.917 --> 00:34:15.119 position:30% line:83% align:start
Look, there it
is!

00:34:53.029 --> 00:34:55.999 position:19% line:83% align:start
The entire asteroid is
covered in flowers...

00:34:56.900 --> 00:34:59.269 position:10% line:83% align:start
Something's coming up behind
us!

00:35:03.307 --> 00:35:04.676 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:35:06.178 --> 00:35:07.746 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:35:07.780 --> 00:35:10.083 position:10% line:89% align:start
Damn it... It's coming back!

00:35:10.984 --> 00:35:12.952 position:19% line:89% align:start
Okay! Let's do this!

00:35:12.986 --> 00:35:13.920 position:38% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:35:14.788 --> 00:35:16.289 position:35% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:35:17.457 --> 00:35:20.262 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sailor Planet...

00:35:22.264 --> 00:35:24.766 position:35% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:35:26.368 --> 00:35:27.836 position:33% line:89% align:start
...Attack!

00:35:31.073 --> 00:35:33.376 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:35:34.343 --> 00:35:35.712 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ugh!

00:35:36.345 --> 00:35:40.151 position:19% line:89% align:start
[yelling and grunting]

00:35:43.354 --> 00:35:46.926 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:35:48.961 --> 00:35:50.197 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sighing]

00:35:52.766 --> 00:35:54.501 position:30% line:89% align:start
What is that?

00:35:54.534 --> 00:35:57.071 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hold on, let me run a scan.

00:36:03.045 --> 00:36:06.081 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's Mamoru! </i>

00:36:06.315 --> 00:36:07.249 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:36:07.282 --> 00:36:07.983 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mamo!

00:36:08.016 --> 00:36:10.186 position:19% line:83% align:start
Wait! This could be a
trap...

00:36:10.220 --> 00:36:11.587 position:38% line:89% align:start
But...!

00:36:11.621 --> 00:36:16.359 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>There's no need to worry</i>
 <i>about that. I would never</i>
 <i>use Mamoru as bait. </i>

00:36:16.392 --> 00:36:17.493 position:33% line:89% align:start
Is that...?

00:36:24.236 --> 00:36:25.804 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:36:31.345 --> 00:36:36.382 position:10% line:77% align:start
I didn't expect you to come
all the way here. Seems I've
underestimated you.

00:36:36.583 --> 00:36:39.921 position:10% line:89% align:start
Fiore! Give Mamo back to us!

00:36:39.954 --> 00:36:43.157 position:5% line:83% align:start
Enough. Relax. I'll return
Mamoru to Earth.

00:36:43.558 --> 00:36:45.327 position:5% line:89% align:start
Just not yet.

00:36:45.361 --> 00:36:46.929 position:21% line:89% align:start
What's that mean?!

00:36:51.467 --> 00:36:53.904 position:10% line:89% align:start
Do you know what these are?

00:36:53.937 --> 00:36:56.340 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>They're seeds from my</i>
 <i>flower. </i>

00:36:56.374 --> 00:37:00.077 position:13% line:77% align:start
When this asteroid reaches
the point at which it's
closest to the Earth...

00:37:00.111 --> 00:37:06.018 position:13% line:77% align:start
...every flower here will
release its seeds, sending
them toward your planet.

00:37:07.452 --> 00:37:12.258 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>Once they arrive there, the</i>
 <i>seeds will bloom... and</i>
 <i>ultimately, overtake the</i>

00:37:12.292 --> 00:37:14.160 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>entire world. </i>

00:37:17.197 --> 00:37:19.367 position:16% line:83% align:start
If that happens, mankind
will-

00:37:19.401 --> 00:37:23.570 position:5% line:77% align:start
That's right. Energy will be
drained from every human,
and they will perish...

00:37:23.604 --> 00:37:25.974 position:10% line:89% align:start
Like we'd let that happen!

00:37:26.608 --> 00:37:27.442 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:37:27.475 --> 00:37:29.444 position:13% line:89% align:start
Damn it! Where'd he go?!

00:37:29.477 --> 00:37:30.413 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:37:30.445 --> 00:37:31.514 position:5% line:89% align:start
Ami, what is it?!

00:37:31.547 --> 00:37:34.318 position:10% line:83% align:start
Be careful, everyone! We're
surrounded by monsters!

00:37:34.650 --> 00:37:36.954 position:35% line:83% align:start
[gasping]
Where?!

00:37:37.422 --> 00:37:41.125 position:24% line:77% align:start
No way...! They're
multiplying fast! There're
so many!

00:37:41.159 --> 00:37:42.260 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:37:47.632 --> 00:37:48.867 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:37:50.403 --> 00:37:51.438 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't tell me...

00:37:56.643 --> 00:38:06.855 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:38:06.888 --> 00:38:14.998 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:38:15.031 --> 00:38:19.003 position:13% line:77% align:start
Sailor Moon! Use Princess
Halation to cleanse this
asteroid.

00:38:19.236 --> 00:38:20.438 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's the only way!

00:38:22.040 --> 00:38:22.806 position:5% line:89% align:start
Got it!

00:38:22.840 --> 00:38:24.676 position:10% line:83% align:start
The rest of us will back her
up!

00:38:24.709 --> 00:38:25.610 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mm!

00:38:27.579 --> 00:38:29.614 position:35% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:38:31.050 --> 00:38:33.253 position:13% line:89% align:start
All right! Let's do this!

00:38:34.488 --> 00:38:36.023 position:33% line:89% align:start
Supreme...

00:38:36.056 --> 00:38:38.359 position:33% line:89% align:start
...Thunder!

00:38:38.393 --> 00:38:41.561 position:35% line:89% align:start
[yelping]

00:38:43.097 --> 00:38:47.002 position:24% line:89% align:start
Crescent... Beam!

00:38:47.336 --> 00:38:51.174 position:30% line:89% align:start
Shine Aqua...

00:38:51.207 --> 00:38:52.375 position:30% line:89% align:start
...Illusion!

00:38:57.047 --> 00:39:00.151 position:38% line:89% align:start
Fire...

00:39:00.184 --> 00:39:03.054 position:35% line:89% align:start
...Soul!

00:39:04.089 --> 00:39:11.197 position:16% line:89% align:start
Moon Princess Halation!

00:39:19.139 --> 00:39:21.708 position:35% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:39:21.742 --> 00:39:25.548 position:5% line:83% align:start
This is bad. At this rate,
all my flowers will wilt.

00:39:25.580 --> 00:39:28.284 position:5% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:39:28.317 --> 00:39:30.219 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:39:30.252 --> 00:39:34.458 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>Careful, everyone! Enemy</i>
 <i>energy's building up in the</i>
 <i>direction of nine o'clock! </i>

00:39:36.660 --> 00:39:37.961 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:39:38.228 --> 00:39:40.664 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:39:48.407 --> 00:39:48.774 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:39:48.807 --> 00:39:50.676 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:39:53.113 --> 00:39:55.148 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:40:00.121 --> 00:40:03.425 position:33% line:89% align:start
[trembling]

00:40:04.792 --> 00:40:08.663 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:40:08.697 --> 00:40:13.803 position:21% line:89% align:start
[crying and digging]

00:40:13.836 --> 00:40:17.341 position:16% line:89% align:start
Rei! Ami! Mako! Minako!

00:40:18.509 --> 00:40:21.211 position:19% line:89% align:start
Please, don't die...

00:40:22.547 --> 00:40:24.415 position:24% line:89% align:start
Such a coward...

00:40:24.449 --> 00:40:25.116 position:38% line:89% align:start
Huh...?

00:40:25.150 --> 00:40:26.117 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:40:26.151 --> 00:40:28.420 position:13% line:83% align:start
You abandoned your friends
to save yourself.

00:40:30.655 --> 00:40:32.324 position:27% line:89% align:start
Moon Princess-

00:40:32.358 --> 00:40:33.726 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Stop! </i>

00:40:36.429 --> 00:40:37.664 position:38% line:89% align:start
Girls!

00:40:40.700 --> 00:40:42.637 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Sailor Moon. </i>

00:40:42.669 --> 00:40:43.671 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh!

00:40:44.606 --> 00:40:46.741 position:10% line:83% align:start
Drop that weapon. Don't harm
my flowers!

00:40:46.774 --> 00:40:48.377 position:30% line:89% align:start
Otherwise...

00:40:49.745 --> 00:40:52.047 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:40:52.282 --> 00:40:53.149 position:44% line:89% align:start
No!

00:40:53.183 --> 00:40:58.489 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:41:02.561 --> 00:41:03.495 position:27% line:89% align:start
Stop, please...

00:41:05.130 --> 00:41:08.833 position:13% line:77% align:start
If you mistreat my flowers
any further, then your friends
will suffer even more.

00:41:08.867 --> 00:41:13.539 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>If you care about them,</i>
 <i>throw down your weapon! </i>

00:41:13.574 --> 00:41:15.141 position:27% line:89% align:start
Sailor Moon...

00:41:15.475 --> 00:41:17.544 position:13% line:83% align:start
You know what you have to
do...

00:41:17.578 --> 00:41:19.913 position:19% line:83% align:start
You must fight, Sailor
Moon...

00:41:19.947 --> 00:41:22.916 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're the only one who can
save Earth now...

00:41:22.950 --> 00:41:25.420 position:10% line:89% align:start
Bring down... the enemy...

00:41:26.387 --> 00:41:28.224 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:41:29.592 --> 00:41:32.861 position:10% line:83% align:start
So, then? Will you turn your
back on your friends?!

00:41:34.264 --> 00:41:35.232 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh!

00:41:43.274 --> 00:41:44.742 position:33% line:89% align:start
You win...

00:41:44.775 --> 00:41:48.747 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm sorry, everyone. But I</i>
 <i>can't do it. </i>

00:41:48.780 --> 00:41:51.684 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I don't want to lose you</i>
 <i>guys again... </i>

00:41:51.718 --> 00:41:53.720 position:19% line:89% align:start
Usagi... You coward!

00:41:53.920 --> 00:41:56.690 position:10% line:89% align:start
I just... I can't bear it...

00:41:56.724 --> 00:41:59.460 position:21% line:83% align:start
I... can't watch you
suffer...

00:41:59.493 --> 00:42:00.561 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:42:06.368 --> 00:42:07.602 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:42:11.240 --> 00:42:13.677 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:42:13.710 --> 00:42:16.280 position:35% line:89% align:start
[fainting]

00:42:16.313 --> 00:42:17.481 position:35% line:89% align:start
You guys!

00:42:17.514 --> 00:42:23.288 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:42:23.321 --> 00:42:28.594 position:10% line:77% align:start
What is with these humans...
And what is this that I'm
feeling...?!

00:42:28.627 --> 00:42:29.794 position:35% line:89% align:start
Fiore...

00:42:29.827 --> 00:42:31.530 position:16% line:89% align:start
Don't let her fool you.

00:42:31.563 --> 00:42:35.834 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>Sailor Moon is a selfish</i>
 <i>girl who's trying to steal</i>
 <i>Mamoru from you. </i>

00:42:36.336 --> 00:42:38.805 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's right... I'm no
fool...!

00:42:38.838 --> 00:42:42.543 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Rest assured, Fiore. I shall</i>
 <i>lend you my power. </i>

00:42:43.344 --> 00:42:49.251 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>If you defeat Sailor Moon,</i>
 <i>Mamoru will remember that</i>
 <i>you are his only friend. </i>

00:42:49.284 --> 00:42:50.352 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh--

00:42:59.862 --> 00:43:02.900 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:43:19.386 --> 00:43:28.464 position:33% line:89% align:start
[straining]

00:43:32.868 --> 00:43:34.236 position:35% line:89% align:start
Usako...

00:43:35.672 --> 00:43:37.808 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ahhhh!

00:43:41.044 --> 00:43:42.713 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:43:42.747 --> 00:43:46.351 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm going to drain every
ounce of energy from you!

00:43:49.020 --> 00:43:57.029 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:43:57.431 --> 00:44:01.602 position:10% line:77% align:start
My flowers are so delighted
that they're getting to
feast on your energy.

00:44:01.635 --> 00:44:06.040 position:10% line:77% align:start
Yes... The liar who tried to
separate Mamoru and me must
die...

00:44:06.775 --> 00:44:10.479 position:19% line:77% align:start
None of you could ever
understand the loneliness
that Mamoru and I had to go

00:44:10.513 --> 00:44:13.616 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>through...You don't even</i>
 <i>know what it's like to be</i>
 <i>alone! </i>

00:44:17.788 --> 00:44:22.125 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Look, Mizuno's studying by</i>
 <i>herself again - as usual! </i>

00:44:22.159 --> 00:44:26.364 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>She's so stuck up 'cause she</i>
 <i>gets good grades. Teacher's</i>
 <i>pet! </i>

00:44:30.469 --> 00:44:34.340 position:10% line:77% align:start
You never had to curse your
own fate for being born into
this world...

00:44:34.641 --> 00:44:36.443 position:16% line:89% align:start
You'd never understand!

00:44:37.477 --> 00:44:40.614 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I heard she hospitalized</i>
 <i>some boys in a fight.</i>

00:44:40.648 --> 00:44:42.683 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Again? She</i>
 <i>wasn't kicked out?</i>

00:44:42.716 --> 00:44:46.588 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>I know. I never wanna go</i>
 <i>near a violent girl like</i>
 <i>her.</i>

00:44:49.658 --> 00:44:54.397 position:10% line:77% align:start
The loneliness of having no
friends. Do you know what
that feels like?!

00:44:54.997 --> 00:44:57.467 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Minako's not very social, is</i>
 <i>she? </i>

00:44:57.501 --> 00:44:59.969 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Yeah, she always says she's</i>
 <i>busy. </i>

00:45:00.002 --> 00:45:03.808 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Wait, I know! Maybe she's a</i>
 <i>superhero like Sailor V! </i>

00:45:03.842 --> 00:45:05.810 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Yeah, right! That's a good</i>
 <i>one! </i>

00:45:05.844 --> 00:45:07.412 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>[laughing]</i>

00:45:10.683 --> 00:45:13.820 position:19% line:83% align:start
The pain and anger of
never being understood!

00:45:13.854 --> 00:45:15.689 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>You just don't</i>
 <i>get it!</i>

00:45:17.156 --> 00:45:19.125 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>There! That's her! </i>

00:45:19.159 --> 00:45:21.127 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>The one who's a psychic? </i>

00:45:21.161 --> 00:45:24.465 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Yeah! Lost rings, wallets,</i>
 <i>whatever! She just guesses</i>

00:45:24.499 --> 00:45:26.835 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>where they are and</i>
 <i>she's always right.</i>

00:45:26.869 --> 00:45:29.771 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Wow... That's kind of</i>
 <i>creepy. </i>

00:45:33.075 --> 00:45:44.655 position:33% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:45:47.692 --> 00:45:49.794 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's time for me to end
this.

00:45:50.595 --> 00:45:54.968 position:21% line:89% align:start
[breathing heavily]

00:45:55.002 --> 00:45:56.168 position:35% line:89% align:start
Now die.

00:45:56.202 --> 00:45:56.837 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>No! </i>

00:45:57.036 --> 00:45:57.704 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:45:57.738 --> 00:45:59.506 position:5% line:89% align:start
Please don't...

00:45:59.540 --> 00:46:02.543 position:5% line:83% align:start
Please don't take Usagi away
from us, we need her.

00:46:02.576 --> 00:46:04.211 position:16% line:89% align:start
She means a lot to us.

00:46:04.244 --> 00:46:06.514 position:24% line:83% align:start
And we can't live
without her.

00:46:08.082 --> 00:46:10.719 position:5% line:83% align:start
She gave us something
precious...

00:46:10.753 --> 00:46:13.589 position:5% line:83% align:start
Something that is absolutely
irreplaceable.

00:46:13.990 --> 00:46:15.559 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's this nonsense?

00:46:16.993 --> 00:46:20.130 position:19% line:77% align:start
 <i>She's just a liar! She</i>
 <i>doesn't give anything, she</i>
 <i>only takes! </i>

00:46:20.163 --> 00:46:21.832 position:5% line:89% align:start
You don't understand.

00:46:21.866 --> 00:46:24.936 position:5% line:83% align:start
If each one of us
hadn't met Usagi...

00:46:24.969 --> 00:46:26.972 position:5% line:89% align:start
...we'd still be all alone!

00:46:30.242 --> 00:46:32.578 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:46:32.611 --> 00:46:37.183 position:21% line:77% align:start
 <i>No! You're all being</i>
 <i>tricked-all of you, even</i>
 <i>Mamoru! </i>

00:46:37.216 --> 00:46:39.118 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>She's deceiving you all!</i>

00:46:39.152 --> 00:46:43.524 position:10% line:83% align:start
Sailor Moon... I was right.
I cannot let you live.

00:46:43.959 --> 00:46:45.894 position:41% line:89% align:start
Die!

00:46:45.927 --> 00:46:47.629 position:35% line:89% align:start
No don't!

00:46:47.662 --> 00:46:49.497 position:33% line:89% align:start
No! Usagi!

00:47:04.983 --> 00:47:06.784 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>This flower is... </i>

00:47:12.057 --> 00:47:13.158 position:33% line:89% align:start
Mamoru...?!

00:47:13.559 --> 00:47:14.794 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:47:14.828 --> 00:47:16.529 position:30% line:89% align:start
Tuxedo Mask!

00:47:17.831 --> 00:47:18.698 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:47:18.732 --> 00:47:21.002 position:30% line:89% align:start
Can't be...!

00:47:24.038 --> 00:47:30.012 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:47:30.045 --> 00:47:32.815 position:35% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:47:37.687 --> 00:47:39.857 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:47:39.890 --> 00:47:41.659 position:10% line:89% align:start
What's the matter, Fiore?!

00:47:41.692 --> 00:47:43.928 position:13% line:83% align:start
Be strong! I'm right here
with you!

00:47:45.262 --> 00:47:47.297 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's all over...

00:47:47.331 --> 00:47:48.800 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>...Mamoru... </i>

00:47:49.367 --> 00:47:52.605 position:13% line:83% align:start
He just- He threw a flower
at me...

00:47:52.638 --> 00:47:53.739 position:35% line:89% align:start
Fiore...

00:47:54.774 --> 00:47:58.812 position:21% line:83% align:start
Mamoru, you- are you
going to abandon me, too?

00:48:17.199 --> 00:48:18.168 position:27% line:89% align:start
The flowers...

00:48:18.200 --> 00:48:19.869 position:16% line:89% align:start
They all disappeared...

00:48:19.903 --> 00:48:21.038 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:48:21.072 --> 00:48:24.041 position:13% line:89% align:start
Then the Earth is saved!

00:48:26.410 --> 00:48:28.013 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:48:38.758 --> 00:48:40.894 position:33% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

00:48:40.928 --> 00:48:45.734 position:13% line:77% align:start
This asteroid has changed
course. Soon, it will fall
to Earth.

00:48:45.767 --> 00:48:49.704 position:13% line:77% align:start
And you no longer have the
power to escape from this
place.

00:48:49.938 --> 00:48:54.110 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's right... If I can't</i>
 <i>have Mamoru, no one can! </i>

00:48:54.143 --> 00:48:56.847 position:24% line:83% align:start
All of you will be
incinerated with me!

00:48:57.246 --> 00:49:01.885 position:21% line:77% align:start
That's fine with me,
Fiore... Even if you die, I
shall still make the

00:49:01.918 --> 00:49:04.088 position:21% line:89% align:start
Earthlings suffer.

00:49:04.122 --> 00:49:06.224 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I won't let that happen! </i>

00:49:15.835 --> 00:49:16.636 position:33% line:89% align:start
No, don't!

00:49:16.669 --> 00:49:19.005 position:16% line:83% align:start
You can't use the Silver
Crystal!

00:49:20.241 --> 00:49:22.009 position:19% line:83% align:start
If you use the Silver
Crystal...

00:49:22.042 --> 00:49:23.811 position:19% line:89% align:start
...you'll die, Usagi!

00:49:25.846 --> 00:49:27.082 position:30% line:89% align:start
No! Don't...!

00:49:27.749 --> 00:49:32.221 position:21% line:83% align:start
I have to, or else I
can't save all of you.

00:49:32.255 --> 00:49:35.792 position:19% line:83% align:start
Don't worry. I'm going
to be just fine.

00:49:35.825 --> 00:49:38.128 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>We'll all go back to Earth</i>
 <i>together. </i>

00:49:38.162 --> 00:49:39.196 position:41% line:89% align:start
Okay?

00:49:42.499 --> 00:49:44.269 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:49:44.301 --> 00:49:45.136 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:49:45.170 --> 00:49:48.940 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:49:48.973 --> 00:49:52.443 position:16% line:77% align:start
So, you want to use this
stone's power to change the
asteroid's course?!

00:49:52.477 --> 00:49:54.312 position:5% line:89% align:start
I won't let you!

00:49:58.251 --> 00:50:01.222 position:13% line:89% align:start
You'll die here, with me.

00:50:04.357 --> 00:50:05.425 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:50:05.458 --> 00:50:07.428 position:10% line:89% align:start
Just what are you afraid of?

00:50:07.962 --> 00:50:09.463 position:19% line:89% align:start
It'll be all right...

00:50:09.497 --> 00:50:12.134 position:24% line:77% align:start
You won't be alone
anymore, I promise.
'Kay?

00:50:13.168 --> 00:50:14.237 position:5% line:89% align:start
Liar!

00:50:14.270 --> 00:50:17.273 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're trying to trick me by
pretending that you care!

00:50:17.507 --> 00:50:18.708 position:44% line:89% align:start
Eh--

00:50:20.077 --> 00:50:22.046 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:50:27.518 --> 00:50:36.495 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:50:45.874 --> 00:50:47.308 position:33% line:89% align:start
Who are...?

00:50:47.876 --> 00:50:49.911 position:19% line:89% align:start
Don't cry. It's okay.

00:50:49.944 --> 00:50:51.213 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

00:50:52.547 --> 00:50:55.451 position:10% line:77% align:start
But my best friend is going
to have to go away really
soon.

00:50:55.484 --> 00:50:59.055 position:10% line:83% align:start
And there's nothing I can do
to help him!

00:50:59.089 --> 00:50:59.789 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>Guess what? </i>

00:50:59.823 --> 00:51:00.957 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:51:00.991 --> 00:51:03.995 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's a special day. I'm
a big sister, now.

00:51:04.295 --> 00:51:09.500 position:10% line:77% align:start
My mommy just had a baby. So
I brought these flowers to
celebrate!

00:51:10.969 --> 00:51:11.870 position:41% line:89% align:start
Here!

00:51:12.104 --> 00:51:13.538 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's for you!

00:51:14.006 --> 00:51:17.210 position:5% line:89% align:start
Wow... Thanks.

00:51:22.082 --> 00:51:25.185 position:13% line:83% align:start
Sailor Moon gave Mamoru a
flower back then...?

00:51:25.419 --> 00:51:26.388 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:51:27.255 --> 00:51:29.456 position:19% line:83% align:start
That rose! It was from
Sailor Moon!

00:51:32.894 --> 00:51:34.397 position:19% line:89% align:start
Just who are you...?

00:51:39.635 --> 00:51:41.071 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's a flower...

00:51:41.405 --> 00:51:44.508 position:13% line:83% align:start
Fiore! Don't let her fool
you! If she does-

00:51:44.541 --> 00:51:46.911 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:51:46.945 --> 00:51:51.383 position:41% line:83% align:start
Fiore!
[screaming]

00:53:00.263 --> 00:53:05.602 position:38% line:89% align:start
Usagi!

00:53:06.070 --> 00:53:07.004 position:35% line:89% align:start
Usako...

00:53:10.008 --> 00:53:13.578 position:13% line:83% align:start
I will protect all of you,
no matter what!

00:53:21.989 --> 00:53:26.528 position:35% line:89% align:start
[staining]

00:53:26.560 --> 00:53:29.064 position:16% line:83% align:start
Please, Legendary Silver
Crystal...

00:53:29.097 --> 00:53:31.633 position:13% line:83% align:start
...bestow more power upon
me...

00:53:31.666 --> 00:53:33.469 position:10% line:89% align:start
Power to protect everyone...

00:53:33.502 --> 00:53:35.637 position:19% line:83% align:start
... so that nobody is
left alone!

00:53:43.280 --> 00:53:46.017 position:24% line:83% align:start
 Come on! We have
to go help her!

00:53:46.350 --> 00:53:49.253 position:16% line:83% align:start
We can do this if we all
work together!

00:53:49.287 --> 00:53:52.091 position:10% line:89% align:start
Right! We will not die here!

00:53:52.124 --> 00:53:54.159 position:10% line:89% align:start
We'll all return to Earth!

00:54:08.609 --> 00:54:12.114 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:54:22.526 --> 00:54:24.128 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh--

00:54:26.230 --> 00:54:31.136 position:5% line:77% align:start
Hey! If you're going to
play, you have to actually
play, you know!

00:54:31.169 --> 00:54:33.272 position:10% line:89% align:start
Okay! Let's have some fun!

00:54:35.774 --> 00:54:37.076 position:35% line:89% align:start
Usagi...

00:54:39.778 --> 00:54:41.014 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sighing]

00:54:41.047 --> 00:54:44.452 position:5% line:77% align:start
I never realized... But
you're actually a super
hard worker.

00:54:44.485 --> 00:54:48.689 position:10% line:83% align:start
Seriously! You only noticed
that now?!

00:54:49.824 --> 00:54:51.092 position:35% line:89% align:start
Usagi...

00:54:54.663 --> 00:54:57.267 position:21% line:83% align:start
That rice ball looks
so good, I can almost--!

00:54:57.300 --> 00:54:59.668 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hold on... Aren't
you afraid of me?

00:54:59.701 --> 00:55:01.237 position:35% line:89% align:start
No, why?

00:55:01.271 --> 00:55:02.272 position:5% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:55:04.341 --> 00:55:05.342 position:35% line:89% align:start
Usagi...

00:55:08.346 --> 00:55:09.514 position:5% line:89% align:start
I don't believe it!

00:55:09.548 --> 00:55:13.486 position:5% line:77% align:start
My hero Sailor V is standing
right here in front of
me...!

00:55:13.519 --> 00:55:14.686 position:24% line:89% align:start
Tadah! That's me!

00:55:15.820 --> 00:55:17.423 position:5% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

00:55:18.524 --> 00:55:19.692 position:35% line:89% align:start
 Usagi...

00:55:42.252 --> 00:55:47.425 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>That's right... My friends</i>
 <i>are always there to give</i>
 <i>me the strength...</i>

00:55:47.458 --> 00:55:49.227 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>... and the courage</i>
 <i>I need.</i>

00:55:49.260 --> 00:55:52.464 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>The Silver Crystal and I can</i>
 <i>grow stronger! </i>

00:55:53.165 --> 00:55:55.467 position:10% line:89% align:start
No one will be alone again!

00:55:55.668 --> 00:55:58.137 position:21% line:89% align:start
Mercury Star Power!

00:55:58.471 --> 00:56:01.274 position:24% line:89% align:start
Mars Star Power!

00:56:01.307 --> 00:56:03.843 position:21% line:89% align:start
Jupiter Star Power!

00:56:03.876 --> 00:56:06.580 position:24% line:89% align:start
Venus Star Power!

00:56:06.814 --> 00:56:11.286 position:21% line:89% align:start
Moon Crystal Power!

00:56:18.461 --> 00:56:21.231 position:33% line:89% align:start
[straining]

00:56:37.416 --> 00:56:39.686 position:5% line:83% align:start
I wonder how they're all
faring up there...

00:56:40.387 --> 00:56:42.922 position:10% line:83% align:start
I just hope they're able to
come back safely...

00:56:42.956 --> 00:56:44.392 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't worry.

00:56:44.425 --> 00:56:48.596 position:10% line:77% align:start
Sailor Moon is like a mother
to us all. I know she'll
protect everyone.

00:56:48.629 --> 00:56:51.433 position:5% line:89% align:start
Chibi-Usa...

00:57:02.446 --> 00:57:08.819 position:10% line:77% align:start
Usagi! Usagi, wake up! Come
on, Usagi! You have to wake
up!

00:57:09.387 --> 00:57:11.890 position:33% line:89% align:start
You liar...

00:57:12.991 --> 00:57:14.893 position:10% line:89% align:start
You said you wouldn't die...

00:57:16.861 --> 00:57:20.966 position:13% line:77% align:start
What's the point of being
saved, if you... aren't with
us?!

00:57:21.668 --> 00:57:25.439 position:5% line:83% align:start
Come on...! Please just open
your eyes, Usagi!

00:57:25.472 --> 00:57:27.542 position:5% line:89% align:start
In the end, we won...

00:57:27.575 --> 00:57:30.578 position:5% line:83% align:start
...but we lost what was most
important to us...

00:57:35.017 --> 00:57:36.485 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Mamoru... </i>

00:57:36.518 --> 00:57:37.587 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:57:39.489 --> 00:57:40.790 position:35% line:89% align:start
Fiore...

00:57:40.824 --> 00:57:45.028 position:5% line:77% align:start
Thank you. Seems... you and
Sailor Moon have saved me
once again.

00:57:45.061 --> 00:57:49.333 position:5% line:77% align:start
Now... I will fulfill the
promise I made to you,
Mamoru...

00:57:50.502 --> 00:57:53.972 position:5% line:83% align:start
 This is the flower of life
that contains my own energy.

00:57:55.040 --> 00:57:56.975 position:5% line:83% align:start
Give its nectar to Sailor
Moon.

00:58:07.421 --> 00:58:10.692 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:58:26.009 --> 00:58:27.478 position:5% line:89% align:start
Mamo...

00:58:27.512 --> 00:58:28.513 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:58:28.546 --> 00:58:29.714 position:38% line:89% align:start
Guys...

00:58:30.748 --> 00:58:32.618 position:5% line:89% align:start
You see?

00:58:32.651 --> 00:58:36.488 position:5% line:83% align:start
I said... I'd protect all of
you no matter what.

00:58:40.527 --> 00:58:45.733 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:58:45.766 --> 00:58:47.735 position:41% line:89% align:start
Usagi!

